[action] He pulls out a string of mice on elastic; lets go; they snap back.

00:00:57.000 --> 00:01:00.000
[action] Moves a chair to reveal a three-foot-high black hole.

00:01:00.000 --> 00:01:02.000
<v Ratcatcher (Graham Chapman)>
